            "jpName": "伝説の語り部",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "有馬記念の人気投票の結果は……1位、ボク！\n早速、出走の決意表明会見を開くと――",
            "enText": "The results of the Arimakinen popular vote \nare in: ……1, Boku! I immediately held a press \nconference to announce my decision to run―",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 97,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 108,
                    "pathId": 1754615444808526556
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 108,
                    "pathId": -7099863823164539828
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1297407293277689089,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "伝説の語り部",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "会場は――人、人、人！！\nなんと……美の化身たるボクを求め、\n幸福を手にした者の多いことか！",
            "enText": "The venue was filled with people, people, \npeople! How many…… have sought me, the \nincarnation of beauty, and found happiness!",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 105,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 195,
                    "pathId": -468850620042763528
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 188,
                    "pathId": 8937740285537719731
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 192659852223009520,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "伝説の語り部",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "臣民たちへ喜びを伝えるため、\nボクは8時間に渡る感謝のオペラを上演した！",
            "enText": "To bring joy to my subjects, I staged an \neight-hour opera of thanksgiving!",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 91,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": 8519303552390835635
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": -2542389881792590709
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5891171730400086764,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "伝説の語り部",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "そして……ボクは忘れていなかった。\n玉座へ共に歩み、導いてくれた大切な存在。\n――そう、君のことを。",
            "enText": "And…… I did not forget. The one \nwho walked with me to the throne \nand guided me. ―Yes, you.",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 110,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 165,
                    "pathId": 2266461078539989683
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 152,
                    "pathId": 7113446859208018992
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2147653898309512185,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "伝説の語り部",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "君の奉仕に、ボクは誓った。\n『有馬記念』を勝利し、その玉座から――\n最優秀トレーナーの栄誉を授与する……と！",
            "enText": "To your service, I have sworn. I vowed to win \nthe Arimakinen, and from that throne… I award \nthe honor of Best Trainer to ……!",
